									By Larry Jones - Posted on: July 28, 2013									



									Stopped at the Stop In #160 in Rich Creek, Va and it is by far the best convienence store that I have been in. The cashiers were very friendly and helpful. Fresh coffee, and nice clean coffee bar. I was very impressed. Asst Manager, Donna, was very helpful with directions, as I was traveling to another town. I will make this my stop every time I come through that area.
You should be proud of that store.
Thank you 
Larry Jones
Huntsville, Alabama 									




 

